text: The 1966–67 Spartan League season was the 49th in the history of Spartan League. The league consisted of 17 teams. ==League table== The division featured 17 teams, 16 from last season and 1 new team: * Berkhamsted, from Athenian League Division Two ==References== 1966-67 9
title: 1966–67 Spartan League
